                            <head>
                                <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                            </head>
                            <p>In a letter of May 2 to Mr. <persName corresp="#p_LFJ1">Lawton</persName>, Mr. <persName corresp="#p_WJE1">Webb</persName> outlined the Department’s revised proposals
                                with regard to economic aid to the Arab States and Israel. It is
                                printed on <ref target="#pg_120">page 120</ref>.</p>
                            <p>For considerable subsequent documentation on aid programs which
                                affected Israel, see <ref target="#pg_1">pages 1</ref> ff.</p>
